---

<Layout title="Blog - GP Trading Academy" description="Artículos y tutoriales sobre Order Flow, SMC, indicadores NinjaTrader 8 y estrategias de trading profesional.">
  <Header />
  <div id="main-content">
  <main class="pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-16 md:pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-mono text-accent bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 rounded-full mb-4">
          Blog
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">
          Aprende Trading <span class="gradient-text">Profesional</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Tutoriales, guías y análisis sobre Order Flow, SMC y las herramientas de la suite GP Trading para NinjaTrader 8.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center mb-10">
        <button class="filter-btn active px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-mono rounded-full border border-white/10 text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:border-accent/30 transition-all" data-filter="all">Todos</button>
        <button class="filter-btn px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-mono rounded-full border border-white/10 text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:border-accent/30 transition-all" data-filter="Herramientas">Herramientas</button>
        <button class="filter-btn px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-mono rounded-full border border-white/10 text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:border-accent/30 transition-all" data-filter="Educación">Educación</button>
        <button class="filter-btn px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-mono rounded-full border border-white/10 text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:border-accent/30 transition-all" data-filter="Ventaja Estadística">Ventaja Estadística</button>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6" id="posts-grid">
        {posts.map((post) => (
          <a href={`/blog/${post.slug}`} class="block glass-card p-6 md:p-8 group hover:ring-1 hover:ring-accent/30 transition-all" data-category={post.category}>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-gray-500 mb-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 text-accent bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 rounded-full">{post.category}</span>
              <span>{post.date}</span>
              <span>· {post.readTime} lectura</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors mb-2">
              {post.title}
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              {post.excerpt}
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-accent group-hover:gap-2 transition-all">
              Leer artículo <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-16">
        <div class="glass-card p-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Nuevos artículos cada semana</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Suscríbete a nuestro canal de YouTube para no perderte ningún contenido.</p>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@GPTradingFX" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-4 px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-primary bg-accent rounded-full hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all min-h-[44px]">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 00-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 00.502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 002.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 002.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/></svg>
            YouTube
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');
      const filter = btn.dataset.filter;
      document.querySelectorAll('#posts-grid > a').forEach(post => {
        if (filter === 'all' || post.dataset.category === filter) {
          post.style.display = '';
        } else {
          post.style.display = 'none';
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  .filter-btn.active {
    color: #00d4aa;
    border-color: #00d4aa;
    background: rgba(0, 212, 170, 0.1);
  }
</style>
